Package: neuroBEAT
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of the Visual and Acoustic Motor Response (VAMR) Assay
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 20226-01-23
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jana", family = "Raab", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jana.raab@ufz.de"), person(given = "Jana", family = "Schor", role = "ctb", email = "jana.schor@ufz.de"), person(given = "Tamara", family = "Tal*", role = "ctb", email = "tamara.tal@ufz.de"), person(given = "Sebastian", family = "Gutsfeld*", role = "aut", email = "sebastian.gutsfeld@ufz.de"))
Description: Tools to preprocess VAMR data, create phase-annotated time-series plots, model time-resolved endpoints with generalized additive (mixed) models, and summarize single-value endpoints. Generates concentration–response curves (AC50/POD) and violin/box plots with emmeans-based contrasts versus control. Includes a CLI and interoperates with ‘tcplfit2’.
SystemRequirements: R (>= 4.4); Conda/Mamba. See environment.yml.
